text: Viktoria Sölkner (born 1905, date of death unknown) was an Austrian diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Austrian female divers Category:Olympic divers of Austria Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
